<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title><%= companyName %> Privacy Policy</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/modern-normalize/3.0.0/modern-normalize.min.css" integrity="sha512-+C4kPVMWGWQkCUEkPslEfufNRpwKcWTT7LdlE4wBBxJPSA8naSXe8j6CvGHqQ3nHFsIFTZXGR/1R4fJHeZDVhg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Inter", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        background: #fafafa;
        color: #1c1c1c;
      }
      header {
        background: #0b5fff;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
      }
      header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      main {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem 3rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }
      h2 {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        font-size: 1.35rem;
      }
      ul {
        padding-left: 1.25rem;
      }
      a {
        color: #0b5fff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      footer {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: #555555;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1><%= companyName %> Privacy Policy</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
      <p>Last updated: <%= lastUpdated %></p>

      <p>
        <%= companyName %> provides AI-assisted junk removal coordination through Messenger, SMS, and email. This policy describes how we collect, use, and protect personal information when you interact with our Stonegate service.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Messages, photos, and attachments you send through Facebook Messenger or SMS.</li>
        <li>Contact details such as your name, phone number, addresses, and email when you provide them.</li>
        <li>Job details and scheduling preferences shared during the quoting process.</li>
        <li>System logs generated by our application for security and troubleshooting.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Generate junk removal quotes and coordinate pickup times.</li>
        <li>Send confirmations, reminders, and updates about your service.</li>
        <li>Improve our pricing rules, scheduling tools, and customer support.</li>
        <li>Maintain service integrity, detect abuse, and comply with legal obligations.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        We share information with service providers that power our application, including OpenAI for language processing, Meta for Messenger delivery, Twilio for SMS, and our managed database and hosting platforms. These providers only use the data to deliver the requested services on our behalf.
      </p>

      <h2>Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        Conversation history, quotes, and booking records are retained for as long as needed to provide services and maintain business records. You can request deletion or a copy of your data at any time using the contact information below.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Choices</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You may request access, correction, or deletion of your information by contacting us.</li>
        <li>You can opt out of SMS reminders by replying "STOP" to any message we send.</li>
        <li>You may pause Messenger communications by muting or blocking our page.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Security</h2>
      <p>
        We secure data in transit using HTTPS and protect stored records with access controls and activity auditing. While no system is perfectly secure, we regularly review our safeguards.
      </p>

      <h2>Children</h2>
      <p>
        Our services are intended for adults coordinating junk removal. We do not knowingly collect personal information from individuals under 13 years of age.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        For privacy questions or requests please email <a href="mailto:<%= contactEmail %>"><%= contactEmail %></a> or call <%= contactPhone %>.
      </p>

      <footer>
        <p>
          If we make material changes to this policy we will update the date above and, when appropriate, notify you through our service channels.
        </p>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
